<h2 id="download" style="text-align:center;border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0">Download Sonic Megamix Mania</h2>

<strong>Version 1.1</strong> is the latest release, with crash fixes, rebalanced levels and improved special stages. You need two things to play: <strong>Sonic Mania Plus on Steam</strong> (the base game, sold separately) and the <strong>Mania Mod Loader</strong> (free). The mod does not work reliably with non-Steam copies of Mania.

