</div>

<div class="details-box">
<h3>How to Install Sonic Megamix Mania</h3>
<div class="details-grid">
<details>
<summary>Windows (Steam)</summary>
<p><strong>1.</strong> Install <strong>Sonic Mania Plus</strong> from Steam if you haven't already.<br><strong>2.</strong> Download the <strong>Mania Mod Loader</strong> and extract it into your Sonic Mania folder (where <code>SonicMania.exe</code> lives).<br><strong>3.</strong> Download <strong>Megamix Mania v1.1</strong> and extract it into the <code>mods</code> folder created by the Mod Loader.<br><strong>4.</strong> Launch <code>SonicManiaModLoader.exe</code> instead of the normal game.<br><strong>5.</strong> In the Mod Manager, enable <strong>Sonic Megamix Mania</strong> and drag it to the top of the list. To play as Amy Rose, also enable her add-on and place it below the main mod.<br><strong>6.</strong> Set the game language to <strong>English</strong> to prevent crashes.</p>
